/>\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1188882/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1188882/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"43d5ccefd99c28c3317d44f0ccbd65f516454bde","tid":1188591,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"59年金庸開明報，61年金庸出倚天屠龍記，倚天入面有個教叫明教，明教有首歌。<br />\n<br />\n焚我殘軀，熊熊聖火。<br />\n生亦何歡，死亦何苦？<br />\n為善除惡，唯光明故。<br />\n喜樂悲愁，皆歸塵土。<br />\n憐我世人，憂患實多！<br />\n憐我世人，憂患實多！<br />\n<br />\n為善除惡，唯光明故，今日嘅明報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd5f58f307c6f3aff66bb8fda710719dd826995","tid":1188591,"uid":32588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e00022d47c6b9d78f09bc328fa97e0d10f75b2b4","tid":1188591,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb42cb9d285ce5ee2bf9a2979cc375ed123b7ac","tid":1188591,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c4036f3dd9ea0b1867df27e92e9863281bd81c","tid":1188591,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"《明報》收皮啦<br />\n日日搵假先知指點江山"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"無得駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:40:48.000Z","msg":"自稱公信力第一<br />\n日日俾個假先知性幻想<br />\nCls<br />\n無睇好耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"無咗「公信第一」好耐啦"}]}